.TH "NAVIGATOR.VENDOR" "3JS" "August 25, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Navigator.vendor \- Navigator: vendor property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The value of the \f[CR]Navigator\f[R] \f[B]\f[CB]vendor\f[B]\f[R]
property is always either \f[CR]\(dqGoogle Inc.\(dq\f[R],
\f[CR]\(dqApple Computer, Inc.\(dq\f[R], or (in Firefox) the empty
string.
.SH VALUE
Either \f[CR]\(dqGoogle Inc.\(dq\f[R],
\f[CR]\(dqApple Computer, Inc.\(dq\f[R], or (in Firefox) the empty
string.
